<p><i><b>The Evil Stairs</b></i> (<a href="/wiki/Hangul" title="Hangul">Hangul</a>: <span lang="ko-Hang" xml:lang="ko-Hang">마의 계단</span>; <a href="/wiki/Revised_Romanization_of_Korean" title="Revised Romanization of Korean">RR</a>: <i><span title="Korean transliteration" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none">Ma-ui gyedan</span></i>; also known as <i><b>The Devil's Stairway</b></i>) is a <a href="/wiki/1964_in_film" title="1964 in film">1964</a> <a href="/wiki/South_Korea" title="South Korea">South Korean</a> mystery film directed by <a href="/wiki/Lee_Man-hee_(film_director)" title="Lee Man-hee (film director)">Lee Man-hee</a>.</p>
<p></p>
